description: The jungle crowds the trail so closely it almost completely obscures it.  A large rhohara plant arches over the path like a greenish-black canopy decorated with the plant's deadly ruby-tipped thorns.  At the base of the rhohara, a bank of large monkey-tail ferns creates a lush carpet that stands as high as a halfling's chest.
